trans-unit.source: Provides an interface for developers to specify custom editing controls that are associated with a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller ett gränssnitt för utvecklare att ange anpassade redigeringskontroller som är associerade med en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface enables you to associate custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls with a server control--such as a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, a user control, or a custom server control.
trans-unit.target: Gränssnittet IWebEditable kan du associera anpassade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>styr med Serverkontrollen--som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll, en användarkontroll eller en anpassad Serverkontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls are contained with an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control, and this zone with its editing controls provides end users with a user interface (UI) for modifying properties, appearance, and behavior on the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller finns med en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontroll och zonen med dess redigeringskontroller ger slutanvändare med ett användargränssnitt (UI) för att ändra egenskaper, utseende och beteende på den associerade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface includes two exposed members.
trans-unit.target: Gränssnittet IWebEditable innehåller två synliga medlemmar.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A> property provides a way for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to get a reference to the associated server control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A>egenskapen är ett sätt för <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller för att hämta en referens till den associerade server för kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method is used to create an instance of each custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> control associated with a server control, and return them as a collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>metoden används för att skapa en instans av varje anpassad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollen som är kopplad till en serverkontroll och returnera dem som en samling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface is already implemented on the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class, although by default this implementation does not associate any custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class.
trans-unit.target: Gränssnittet IWebEditable har redan implementerats i den grundläggande <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>class, även om som standard den här implementeringen inte associera anpassade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klass.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To associate a derived <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control with custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls, you can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Associera en härledd <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen med anpassade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller, som du kan åsidosätta den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls associated with a server control that implements the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en mängd med anpassade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller som är associerade med en serverkontroll som implementerar det <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable"> </xref> gränssnitt.

trans-unit.source: The CreateEditorParts method enables you to create a collection of all the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls associated with your custom control, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, or user control, and return them as an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateEditorParts kan du skapa en samling för ett anpassat <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller som är associerade med din anpassade kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll eller användaren styr och returnera dem som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control takes the collection and creates instances of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls whenever the server control enters edit mode.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen tar samlingen och skapar instanser av alla de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller när Serverkontrollen anger redigeringsläge.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Typically you implement this method in a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control by overriding its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Vanligtvis du implementera den här metoden i en anpassad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll genom att åsidosätta dess <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A>metod.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In the method, you create instances of the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls you want to associate with your controls, add them to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object, and then return that object.
trans-unit.target: I den här metoden skapar du instanser av anpassat <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller som du vill koppla till din kontroller, lägga till dem i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objektet och returnerar sedan det objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls is then assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Insamling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller sedan tilldelas den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A>egenskapen för den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>zon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> that is added to the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in an implementation of the CreateEditorParts method must have a value assigned to its ID property, otherwise an exception will be thrown when the collection is assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alla <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>som har lagts till i samlingen för <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller i en implementering av metoden CreateEditorParts måste ha ett värde som tilldelats dess ID-egenskap, annars ett undantag genereras när mängden tilldelas den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> that contains the collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls associated with a server control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> som innehåller samlingen av anpassade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller som är associerade med en serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control, user control, or custom control that will be edited by <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en referens till den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll, användarkontroll eller anpassad kontroll som ska redigeras av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The WebBrowsableObject property provides a way for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to get a reference to the server controls they are associated with.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen WebBrowsableObject är ett sätt för <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller för att hämta en referens till serverkontroller som de hör till.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Although the property itself is read-only, the object reference that it returns enables <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to change values in the server control.
trans-unit.target: Även om egenskapen själv är skrivskyddad, objektreferensen som returneras kan <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller för att ändra värden i Serverkontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An object reference to the control associated with an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En objektreferens till kontrollen som är associerade med en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroll.
